Name: ftw.htmlblock
Version: 1.1.3
Summary: A block rendering unescaped HTML to be used on a content page powered by ftw.simplelayout
Home-page: https://github.com/4teamwork/ftw.htmlblock
Author: 4teamwork AG
Author-email: mailto:info@4teamwork.ch
